	   <tr><td colspan=2> The pure wisdom casters are often referred to as the 'Priest' classes as many items in the game are usable by just those three. They also need the same gems for their velious quest armor pieces and are lumped into the 'Priest' category. Necros, mages, wizzys, and chantys are referred to as the 'Caster' classes, etc.&nbsp;&nbsp;Hope this helps clarify things a bit for ya )<br>&nbsp;<br>Brakiss VonKuellar<br>High Priest of the 61st order, Sacred Circle of Life, Vazaelle<br><br>...be who you want to seem...<br><br><br><br><br></td></tr>
